Detailed Description

cvmx_lmc::_wodt_ctl0

LMC_WODT_CTL0 = LMC Write OnDieTermination control See the description in LMC_WODT_CTL1.

Notes: Together, the LMC_WODT_CTL1 and LMC_WODT_CTL0 CSRs control the write ODT mask. See LMC_WODT_CTL1.
